tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE customer_feedback_interactions (
  interaction_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  customer_id INT NOT NULL,
  feedback_text TEXT,
  timestamp TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
  INDEX idx_customer_id (customer_id),
  INDEX idx_timestamp (timestamp)
);

CREATE TABLE CustomerFeedbackInteractions (
  feedback_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  customer_id INT,
  interaction_date DATE,
  interaction_type VARCHAR(255),
  interaction_score INT
)

CREATE TABLE CustomerFeedbackInteractions (
id INT PRIMARY KEY,
feedback TEXT,
timestamp TIMESTAMP,
INDEX idx_timestamp (timestamp)
)

CREATE TABLE CustomerInteractions (
id INT PRIMARY KEY,
customer_id INT,
interaction_type TEXT,
interaction_timestamp TIMESTAMP,
INDEX idx_customer_id (customer_id)
)

CREATE TABLE FeedbackSentiments (
id INT PRIMARY KEY,
feedback_id INT,
sentiment TEXT,
sentiment_score FLOAT,
INDEX idx_feedback_id (feedback_id)
)

CREATE TABLE CustomerFeedbackInteractions (
    feedback_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    feedback_text TEXT,
    customer_id INT,
    interaction_time TIMESTAMP,
    INDEX cust_id_idx (customer_id)
)

CREATE TABLE CustomerFeedbackSentiments (
    feedback_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    sentiment_score FLOAT,
    sentiment_category VARCHAR(50),
    INDEX score_idx (sentiment_score)
)

CREATE TABLE CustomerFeedbackTags (
    feedback_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    tag_name VARCHAR(50),
    INDEX tag_idx (tag_name)
)

CREATE TABLE CustomerFeedbackAnalytics (
    feedback_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    analytics_data JSONB,
    INDEX analytics_idx (feedback_id)
)

CREATE TABLE CustomerFeedbackInteractions (
    feedback_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_id INT,
    interaction_type VARCHAR,
    timestamp TIMESTAMP
)

CREATE TABLE CustomerInteractionsDetails (
    interaction_id INT PRIMARY KEY,

    interaction_text TEXT,

)

CREATE TABLE CustomerDetails (
    customer_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_name VARCHAR,
    customer_email VARCHAR,
    customer_phone VARCHAR
)

CREATE TABLE FeedbackSentiments (
    sentiment_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    feedback_id INT,
    sentiment_score FLOAT
)

CREATE TABLE IndexOptimizations (
    index_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    schema_name VARCHAR,
    optimization_type VARCHAR,
    optimization_timestamp TIMESTAMP
)
